entries.title_d: During the attacks on the crippled shuttle, the Rebel pilots where sending signals to what appears to be a command vessel. Hunt down that vessel and inspect it for any information that we can find useful.
entries.title: Dathomir System: Inspect the Rebel Command Vessel
entries.split_quest_alert: Nice work, pilot. Fly that information back to the Naboo system for immediate transfer to a shuttle.
entries.quest_location_d: The Rebel command vessel appears to still be in the Dathomir system. You will be supplied with a navigation waypoint to its most recent location.
entries.quest_inspect_d: Disable the Rebel command vessel and inspect it for any information on the Rebel operations in the system.
entries.quest_dock_d: Dock with the Rebel command vessel and transfer the reports to your vessel.
